# Cyclone

## Cloud infrastructure system that provides a platform for cloud-native applications and workflows.

Cyclone is an on-premises cloud infrastructure system that provides a platform for cloud-native applications and workflows. The system uses OpenStack to integrate disparate hardware into a flexible and diverse pool of resources that can be leveraged to deploy software systems at scale.

### System Specifications

| Cyclone provides 2,944 CPU cores, 8.3 TB RAM, and 145.5 TB of backing storage. |
